|                                             | of model resources is enabled.             |                        |
*---------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------+------------------------+
| <<<modletLocation>>>                        | The class path location searched for       | No. {{{E}[E]}}         |
|                                             | modlets.                                   |                        |
*---------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------+------------------------+
| <<<modletResourceValidationEnabled>>>       | A flag indicating JAXP schema validation   | No. Defaults to true.  |
|                                             | of modlet resources is enabled.            |                        |
